title: Blood-CS_500_D00
extract_protocol: Total RNA was extracted from PAXgene tubes according to the manufacturerâ€™s instructions. In brief, total RNA was isolated using the PAXgene blood RNA kit (PreAnalytix, Hilden, Germany). The residual genomic DNA was digested using the RNase-Free DNase set (Qiagen Valencia, CA, USA).
label: biotin
label_protocol: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hybridization_protocol: Following fragmentation, cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on Human GeneChip U133 Plus 2.0 Array. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the GeneArray Scanner G3000.
description: Gene expression data from whole blood
data_processing: The data were normalized using RMA methods.
